<P>
   COXNET-WRESTLING PAGE
</P>
<P>
   The weekly CoxNet wrestling page is available Wednesdays by 11
a.m. EST. Keying to the Monday wrestling events, It's good for
publication any day through Sunday. Here are the elements on the
page, which are also moving on the entertainment wire:
</P>
<P>
   WRESTLING-FEATURE _ A feature on a wrestler or issue. This week:
(Cox News Service) WITH PHOTOS.
</P>
<P>
   WRESTLING-COLUMN _ Our columnist John Allen writes about a trend
or issue in pro wrestling. This week: (Allen, Cox News Service)
</P>
<P>
   WRESTLING-GRAPEVINE _ News and gossip from the wrestling world.
(Allen, Cox News Service)
</P>
<P>
   WRESTLING-RAIL _ Brief items of interest, including bios, TV
info, etc. (Allen, Cox News Service)
</P>
