<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-03-08 15:24 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A0669 &Cx1f; tab-z
r p BC-INSURGENTS-LOSS-INDEP     03-08 1319
