<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-03-08 16:24 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A0736 &Cx1f; taf-z
u p BC-BRADLEY-NYT &LR;      03-08 0533
