   - Women's Sports &AMP; Fitness reports that when  &UR; Brooke Shields &LR; 
and  &UR; Andre Agassi  &LR; were married, he taped a photograph of  &UR; Steffi &LR; 
 &UR; Graf &LR;  _ Agassi's current girlfriend _ on their refrigerator to
remind Shields to get into shape.
