<HEADLINE>
HEARING OPENS ON PLANS TO FUND COLOMBIA   DRUG FIGHT 
</HEADLINE>
  
 (i and w coding)   (For use by New York Times News Service clients)  
 By JOHN DONNELLY  
 c.2000 The Boston Globe  
 
<TEXT>
<P>
   WASHINGTON _ The war on drugs may approach a moment of truth
Thursday.
</P>
<P>
   It is set to happen in room 2359 at the Rayburn Building, when
House Appropriations Committee Chair C.W. Bill Young of Florida
