<P>
   CONG27-FOLLOW _ Follow-up on the 27th congressional election,
which already looks like the most interesting congressional race in
November: James Rogan vs. Adam Schiff. By Jennifer Hamm. (Will run
in the ``a'' national and ``n'' California news files.)
</P>
