Housing Affordability Index feel to its lowest level since 1992
last year, a Realtors group said. Housing affordability in the
state dropped from 40 percent in 1998 to 37 percent in 1999. The 3
percentage point drop is the biggest since 1989. By Jason
Takenouchi. (Will run in the ``f'' financial news file.)
</P>
