   &UR; GLOBAL WATER CRISIS THREATENS US ALL &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   There is a serious water crisis developing in many parts of the
world. Increased flooding and droughts are a symptom. But do the
technical experts and the politicians understand where the solution
really lies? Such urgent questions will be discussed in the
forthcoming Global Water Forum at The Hague from March 17 to 22. &QL;
</P>
