<HEADLINE>
 
</HEADLINE>
  
 Wednesday, March 8, 2000   Editors  
   
<TEXT>
<P>
   The Hearst News Service has filed or will file the following for
Thursday. If you have questions, please call Susie McBee or Tim
Spence at 202-298-6920.
</P>
<P>
   &LR;  &QL;
